workflow ScopeLeadJob: "Your Job"
    "Read the operator brief before you touch the repo."
    "Pick the smallest fix path and write the repair plan to `artifacts/repair_plan.md`."
    "If a later reader needs a short note that does not belong in the repair plan or final JSON, use `rally-kernel`."
    "When the review passes later, read the accepted test report and close the run instead of reopening the same work."
